<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-8-common-myths-about-back-pain/">Mayo Clinic Q&amp;amp;A: 8 common myths about back pain</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
